    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roasted vegetables</strong> to the pot with the <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and cook over a medium heat for 4-5 min</p><p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half and add to a baking tray, cut side up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until they're hot and crusty</p>",
