      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pot from the heat and roughly blitz everything up with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong>, leaving some chunks for texture – this is your <strong>tangy tomato soup</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>warmed ciabatta halves</strong> from the oven</p>",
